{
  "message": "fuzz(ext4-integrity): add 16 structured corpus seeds\n\nCoverage expansion for fuzz_verify_ext4_integrity harness:\n- All 6 SeedImage modes: Raw, Clean, Dirty, CorruptSuperblock,\n  CorruptGroupDesc, Truncated\n- max_inodes edge cases: 0, small (1-8), medium (1-32), u32::MAX\n- Mutation variants: no mutations, single focused, 15 focused, wide\n- Dirty image with orphan inode flag re-application\n- Raw mode with valid ext4 magic header\n- Truncated to near-zero length\n- Targeted mutations at state and magic offsets\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
